Jordan James Spence -LRB- born 24 May 1990 -RRB- is an English footballer who plays for Ipswich Town .
Predominantly as a right-back , Spence can also operate as a centre-back .
He has represented and captained England at various youth levels .
He has previously played for West Ham United , Leyton Orient , Scunthorpe United , Bristol City , Sheffield Wednesday and Milton Keynes Dons .